{"tid":446993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大國青年：咱們的人生不用供樓","createTime":"2017-10-25T00:29:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-30T04:20:46.000Z","uid":35519,"like":19,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"1350e19d6eff6794e0950ebb71480ed25b5caa95","tid":446993,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T00:29:14.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大國青年：咱們的人生不用供樓</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.cup.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/rsz_2016-06-23t121449z_1564750882_s1aetlodanab_rtrmadp_3_china-property-1200x600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F07%2Frsz_2016-06-23t121449z_1564750882_s1aetlodanab_rtrmadp_3_china-property-1200x600.jpg&h=e21be085&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有一日，港中青年同枱食飯，談及兩地物業價格&mdash;&mdash;香港青年說：「在 30 歲前要供完一層樓，不只是夢想，更是幻想。」中國青年答：「供樓？咱們的人生不用供樓。」雖然以上對話純屬虛構，但根據研究，中國青年的確沒供樓煩惱。<br />\n<br />\nBusiness Insider 引述了 Yougov 和 Bernstein 的調查報告，分析指，在 700 名 18 至 29 歲的受訪中國青年中，有近半數至少擁有一間物業，而且沒因買樓而欠債。<br />\n<br />\nBernstein 解釋，中國青年能夠如此高速上車，是多得「父母銀行」的眷顧，「一如其他調查，在 700 位 18 至 29 歲的受訪者中總有一些網絡百萬富翁。可是，不論是一線、二線還是三線城市，那些擁有物業又沒負債的青年，都是依靠父母的金錢置業。」他又指，「跨代財富轉移（Intergenerational wealth transfer）的現象不單是理論和預測，而是正在發生。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.cup.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/china_property_1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F06%2Fchina_property_1.png&h=9735471e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.cup.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/china_property_2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F06%2Fchina_property_2.png&h=19ba40fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBernstein 認為，報告對中國經濟來說是好消息，因為它反映中國不會因人們供款能力下降而出現房債泡沫爆破。「這使我們對中國房地產市場的發展變得樂觀。目前，外界不少聲音認為中國最有可能爆破的泡沫就是物業市場，尤其是一線城市的物業市場。」<br />\n<br />\n他補充，「樓價可負擔指數（平均樓價與平均年收入的比例）不但較去年上升三分之二，居住在二、三線城市的市民負擔能力亦都提升。從受訪者的數據可見，居住在一線城市的青年較有可能在 29 歲前擁有自己的物業。」<br />\n<br />\n這份報告除了是衡量中國經濟在來年會否「支爆」的指標，也是對香港青年的最大諷刺。香港的樓價冠絕世界，全球共知，數之不盡的港人，分幾十年才供完（幾）百呎樓，這些悲慘生活，在真正贏在起跑線的中國青年眼中，應是完全無法理解的人生。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cup.com.hk/2016/07/04/many-young-people-in-china-own-their-houses-debt-free/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2F2016%2F07%2F04%2Fmany-young-people-in-china-own-their-houses-debt-free%2F&d=Q8pdFaTDdXkZv1Z8oTHUCWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=a107a157\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cup.com.hk/2016/07/04/many-young-people-in-china-own-their-houses-debt-free/</a>"},{"pid":"df261e2115a724ce71ae1bb16257572bcda8e046","tid":446993,"uid":70292,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T00:32:36.000Z","msg":"沒有負債煩惱，係錯既。<br />\n<br />\n應該係人生都沒有煩惱了。"},{"pid":"d3836a5e22c9336b4da36ddd1b7bab03b2fde67e","tid":446993,"uid":80153,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T00:33:03.000Z","msg":"港豬以做根奴為榮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0082c84c3d8a50fafa3dd19e6090c50c99f0476","tid":446993,"uid":22701,"like":46,"dislike":3,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T00:56:02.000Z","msg":"我們的人生不用翻牆"},{"pid":"4f132e012764b4f7180764970b2f2dc3cfe5a592","tid":446993,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T00:57:43.000Z","msg":"中港交流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中港融合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deea7383afc77a508170bcb6ad5e3c75ec7ba6fe","tid":446993,"uid":86841,"like":4,"dislike":12,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T00:59:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"121dddc2a756dda250a1927ee4c8efd861691e03","tid":446993,"uid":23833,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T01:00:07.000Z","msg":"港豬戇鳩鳩<br />\n<br />\n同一價錢，唔同大細"},{"pid":"2ad5e2db56d96bd28b08e631f3f496bf01b38ba7","tid":446993