/>\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你講依家係幾時開始？<br />\n我前排仲聽到村民同公安打架嘅news喎"},{"pid":"574d2d13ccf2111b3bf98ad7270cd7df592e19ae","tid":446993,"uid":44243,"like":6,"dislike":9,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T01:24:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登真係好撚多五毛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地講句唔岩聽就5毛，死撚左去啦"},{"pid":"92a5ee9ec9d4cf52cc3f38a3bc9040829fbe6345","tid":446993,"uid":63846,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T01:25:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>住貴州，內蒙梗唔洗供樓<br />\n不如問下上海，北京啲青年有冇供樓煩惱</blockquote><br />\n冇，正統上海北京人都有幾層樓<br />\n<br />\n仲要係一孩<br />\n<br />\n窮的係外地人"},{"pid":"10fc48816ae745d33a23efa0ef834a29d9b02d43","tid":446993,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T01:28:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>會唔會畀中共強收樓先？<br />\n佢哋話發展就是硬道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家大陸收樓收地政府比錢<br />\n大把農民變土豪<br />\n邊似得港共<br />\n燒樓強拆收地<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你講依家係幾時開始？<br />\n我前排仲聽到村民同公安打架嘅news喎</blockquote><br />\n真係睇個官貪幾多， 怕煩唔算大貪又可以賺大錢咪賠得多人地自然自願搬走， 有d就賺得少貪多d山高皇帝遠咪強拆賠都唔洗賠"},{"pid":"672c0d4eb616a909fd93b8e609a8ad9f01bb5b91","tid":446993,"uid":128210,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T01:29:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>會唔會畀中共強收樓先？<br />\n佢哋話發展就是硬道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家大陸收樓收地政府比錢<br />\n大把農民變土豪<br />\n邊似得港共<br />\n燒樓強拆收地<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你講依家係幾時開始？<br />\n我前排仲聽到村民同公安打架嘅news喎</blockquote><br />\n成日都有<br />\n得閒上大陸網站睇，<br />\n好多人改晒做笑話tim<br />\n不過有分別，<br />\n你係當地原本係到的人（起碼住左幾十年），咁就有得賠，而且唔少tim 。<br />\n你係外來人，好似on9 香港人反上去買樓的，強拆，分反豆零比你。<br />\n簡單而言，欺善怕惡。<br />\n死都唔好反大陸買樓。"},{"pid":"87a8b1befe3147a2642f560c7051d6604e57c179","tid":446993,"uid":10692,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T01:31:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1a3aa9fd5740cd85bc11c4dcbf7cc9dcb9ca1be0","tid":446993,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T01:33:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>住貴州，內蒙梗唔洗供樓<br />\n不如問下上海，北京啲青年有冇供樓煩惱</blockquote><br />\n冇，正統上海北京人都有幾層樓<br />\n<br />\n仲要係一孩<br />\n<br />\n窮的係外地人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我鄉下的親戚都係咁。<br />\n表哥有3仔女。<br />\n2個大女嫁左。<br />\n一個仔，已經有一棟舖（3層）同一棟樓（3層）比佢。<br />\n不過價值好低者。<br />\n舖都係200萬內，樓應該再低d 。"},{"pid":"ee33fc96230731b4ff565f020dca96e84cd22492","tid":446993,"uid":38472,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T01:41:55.000Z","msg":"屌，支那地大，正常都有樓啦。"},{"pid":"55ab32680344c9a64557aa69e7e3d637b5e5b676","tid":446993,"uid":50533,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T01:46:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dfc5ea045ce45dd71fcfab0e423ba4468069cf10","tid":446993,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T01:50:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>會唔會畀中共強收樓先？<br />\n佢哋話發展就是硬道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家大陸收樓收地政府比錢<br />\n大把農民變土豪<br />\n邊似得港共<br />\n燒樓強拆收地<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你講依家係幾時開始？<br />\n我前排仲聽到村民同公安打架嘅news喎</blockq