><br />\n講呢d顯得好自卑好葡萄"},{"pid":"13ad18e49175118959b9dbd335078552b10690ee","tid":446993,"uid":112627,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T02:04:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>連登真係好撚多五毛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地講句唔岩聽就5毛，死撚左去啦</blockquote><br />\n唔岩聽就話人五毛on99<br />\n要層樓要翻牆上網同冇樓任上網你簡咩先<br />\n香港住方面係柒啊ma 同人鬥慘好撚有意思咩"},{"pid":"8a41c41168fa164a868aa890c953e7b87eecda14","tid":446993,"uid":37808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T02:04:36.000Z","msg":"深圳啲樓呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf758b4b1c4a0b95076dbf63f3ddf5ee4d2980b2","tid":446993,"uid":85163,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T02:04:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f52b2f751ad5e11591d300d7be5928a23aef38c","tid":446993,"uid":112627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T02:15:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我們的人生不用翻牆</blockquote><br />\n過多十年你j都冇得打</blockquote><br />\n講呢d顯得好自卑好葡萄</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好葡萄港仔打十幾年工儲首期?</blockquote><br />\n中六合彩我都比曬老細叫佢唔好炒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等我可以做野儲首期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c67d474a3d6a3500c9190e1a20dbed6b4f3a95c2","tid":446993,"uid":37735,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T02:28:43.000Z","msg":"講再多都好<br />\n<br />\n寧死唔做支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"545613849ccbe0797b7ee7d340c6b58a6d07b4a3","tid":446993,"uid":28309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T02:29:46.000Z","msg":"sad but true<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfade5ac4d14f4d098a41d7a90703e1ed6cf17df","tid":446993,"uid":53687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T02:31:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>會唔會畀中共強收樓先？<br />\n佢哋話發展就是硬道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家大陸收樓收地政府比錢<br />\n大把農民變土豪<br />\n邊似得港共<br />\n燒樓強拆收地<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你講依家係幾時開始？<br />\n我前排仲聽到村民同公安打架嘅news喎</blockquote><br />\n魚蛋雨傘夠有啦<br />\n唔見你講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n九唔搭八<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9bb8121adfd2dc68330612b25843547ad9de4cf","tid":446993,"uid":37735,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T02:35:55.000Z","msg":"五毛狗水準 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係咁易置業 之前蝸居就唔會咁大回響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家支那人講緊上海天天律北京深圳 呢堆<br />\n置業同香港難度無分別<br />\n<br />\n其他2，3 線城市 鄉下 係好易置業<br />\n但攞來同香港比<br />\n<br />\n你比面積 比價值<br />\n你唔講底特律 1蚊買樓 (係啊要 比維修，律師費 但肯定平過支國2 3線)<br />\n<br />\n你真係認真  我貼返美國樓vs 支那樓<br />\n<br />\n人地幾十萬 幾千尺大屋 仲有私人遊泳池"},{"pid":"c13739e56b55a8b77b1c2f1edf75a29935fdcfe3","tid":446993,"uid":985,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T02:36:44.000Z","msg":"事實係人地壓力細好多。<br />\n就算老豆老母住鄉下，都嘔到幾十個俾仔女係一線二線城市買樓。<br />\n一孩政策，養一個壓力又細。<br />\n係香港窮到住公屋，大陸新移民係大陸都有樓啦。<br />\n地方政府有地分，佢地一定會自己起樓。<br />\n近珠三角，一收地又發達。"},{"pid":"cec65ef3a7be9e915979d2aff01ee23d7189dc5b","tid":446993,"uid":84128,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T02:43:48.000Z","msg":"要奶共了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1781ca6991efd50d01510879db0a0d30df6b1860","tid":446993,"uid":66499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:42:59.000Z","msg":"都係睇地方<br />\n好耐之前先唔係有集叫蝸居嘅電視劇講 上樓嘅煩惱咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddf1c5d989b6d99dbe872ea9d429e826073ff92a","tid":446993,"uid":45353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:48:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>會唔會畀中共強收樓先？<br />\n佢哋話發展就是硬道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家大陸收樓收地政府比錢<br />\n大把農民變土豪<br />\n邊似得港共<br />\n燒樓強拆收地<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係個個有錢收<br />\n<br />\n年中就唔會咁多人為強收上京申寃"},{"pid":"91270f3a679c5b4f42b4e7921f4bc0e53198a492","tid":446993,"uid":50533,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T06:35:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d1e13b4f5b0b819d2892c0994ebac71d7101b34","tid":446993,"uid":83016,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T06:40:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我們的人生不用翻牆</blockquote><br />\n我情願日日翻牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b6863f89dc328075a1317d76053eafe9f5bc318","tid":446993,"uid":50533,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T06:42:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"de458f4dbe4c5302fd0d5494434fe05e814e0a2d","tid":446993,"uid":112627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T08:52:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>50萬連登仔就可以放棄民主<br />\n翻牆又有咩所謂</blockquote><br />\n民主目的係咩？"},{"pid":"a4d7225ec877cdcf66eacac502e21e51caa2ffd1","tid":446993,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T09:10:35.000Z","msg":"鄰國果代人一孩政策，差唔多2家人d資源俾哂呢代d青年，而家緊係唔愁供樓，到佢地老豆老母退休要供養咪又一樣，當然鄰國人冇血性可能唔養都唔奇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d3ea6bf6abf2e1d657ed81043d2cf13c3715f26","tid":446993,"uid":80294,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T09:25:58.000Z","msg":"我上深圳 廣洲 睇樓盤 無論由班契弟agents 到租客， 業主 都同我講緊另一個story 囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87dfcb17161d89f87a7693f5ddb5faab989ac564","tid":446993,"uid":63846,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T10:15:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鄰國果代人一孩政策，差唔多2家人d資源俾哂呢代d青年，而家緊係唔愁供樓，到佢地老豆老母退休要供養咪又一樣，當然鄰國人冇血性可能唔養都唔奇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上一代大陸人基本上都有退休金"},{"pid":"3973732e434b4447705ca37cec8ea4b4f6638bcf","tid":446993,"uid":56459,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T10:20:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>鄰國果代人一孩政策，差唔多2家人d資源俾哂呢代d青年，而家緊係唔愁供樓，到佢地老豆老母退休要供養咪又一樣，當然鄰國人冇血性可能唔養都唔奇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上一代大陸人基本上都有退休金</blockquote><br />\n有社保 有退休金<br />\n仲好過香港"},{"pid":"abce4998b6d3387f4c39113329fda4a16a855657","tid":446993,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T10:24:07.000Z","msg":"支國出哂名幾代供一間屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21ac8382b317ddda1f55a535c364c4e67ee98ab1","tid":446993,"uid":28378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T10:29:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大國青年：咱們的人生不用供樓</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.cup.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/rsz_2016-06-23t121449z_1564750882_s1aetlodanab_rtrmadp_3_china-property-1200x600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F07%2Frsz_2016-06-23t121449z_1564750882_s1aetlodanab_rtrmadp_3_china-property-1200x600.jpg&h=e21be085&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有一日，港中青年同枱食飯，談及兩地物業價格&mdash;&mdash;香港青年說：「在 30 歲前要供完一層樓，不只是夢想，更是幻想。」中國青年答：「供樓？咱們的人生不用供樓。」雖然以上對話純屬虛構，但根據研究，中國青年的確沒供樓煩惱。<br />\n<br />\nBusiness Insider 引述了 Yougov 和 Bernstein 的調查報告，分析指，在 700 名 18 至 29 歲的受訪中國青年中，有近半數至少擁有一間物業，而且沒因買樓而欠債。<br />\n<br />\nBernstein 解釋，中國青年能夠如此高速上車，是多得「父母銀行」的眷顧，「一如其他調查，在 700 位 18 至 29 歲的受訪者中總有一些網絡百萬富翁。可是，不論是一線、二線還是三線城市，那些擁有物業又沒負債的青年，都是依靠父母的金錢置業。」他又指，「跨代財富轉移（Intergenerational wealth transfer）的現象不單是理論和預測，而是正在發生。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.cup.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/china_property_1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F06%2Fchina_property_1.png&h=9735471e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.cup.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/china_property_2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F06%2Fchina_property_2.png&h=19ba40fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Bernstein</span></strong> 認為，報告對中國經濟來說是好消息，因為它反映中國不會因人們供款能力下降而出現房債泡沫爆破。「這使我們對中國房地產市場的發展變得樂觀。目前，外界不少聲音認為中國最有可能爆破的泡沫就是物業市場，尤其是一線城市的物業市場。」<br />\n<br />\n他補充，「樓價可負擔指數（平均樓價與平均年收入的比例）不但較去年上升三分之二，居住在二、三線城市的市民負擔能力亦都提升。從受訪者的數據可見，居住在一線城市的青年較有可能在 29 歲前擁有自己的物業。」<br />\n<br />\n這份報告除了是衡量中國經濟在來年會否「支爆」的指標，也是對香港青年的最大諷刺。香港的樓價冠絕世界，全球共知，數之不盡的港人，分幾十年才供完（幾）百呎樓，這些悲慘生活，在真正贏在起跑線的中國青年眼中，應是完全無法理解的人生。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cup.com.hk/2016/07/04/many-young-people-in-china-own-their-houses-debt-free/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2F2016%2F07%2F04%2Fmany-young-people-in-china-own-their-houses-debt-free%2F&d=Q8pdFaTDdXkZv1Z8oTHUCWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=a107a157\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cup.com.hk/2016/07/04/many-young-people-in-china-own-their-houses-debt-free/</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n舊登有條友個user呢就係叫Bernstein, 人民幣大好友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c09a1ab37a810c35a9491dae128ca18613cedd","tid":446993,"uid":43189,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T12:34:46.000Z","msg":"五毛又要開始吹奏支那，根本支那貧富懸殊就拍得住香港<br />\n大城市你無家族/父母支持邊有咁易買到樓"},{"pid":"adf9b1680ed353e807bed2aa2ee5c6561e2d1c75","tid":446993,"uid":85163,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T12:36:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bcd7e2a9cd420d02a7fc3bd1413c109d829a412d","tid":446993,"uid":72736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T13:23:34.000Z","msg":"政府強收咪冇囉，地都唔係你既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cc83274751d7fac28381b3cf8b1181b3e4dce8d","tid":446993,"uid":98163,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T13:25:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大國青年：咱們的人生不用供樓</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.cup.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/rsz_2016-06-23t121449z_1564750882_s1aetlodanab_rtrmadp_3_china-property-1200x600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F07%2Frsz_2016-06-23t121449z_1564750882_s1aetlodanab_rtrmadp_3_china-property-1200x600.jpg&h=e21be085&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有一日，港中青年同枱食飯，談及兩地物業價格&mdash;&mdash;香港青年說：「在 30 歲前要供完一層樓，不只是夢想，更是幻想。」中國青年答：「供樓？咱們的人生不用供樓。」雖然以上對話純屬虛構，但根據研究，中國青年的確沒供樓煩惱。<br />\n<br />\nBusiness Insider 引述了 Yougov 和 Bernstein 的調查報告，分析指，在 700 名 18 至 29 歲的受訪中國青年中，有近半數至少擁有一間物業，而且沒因買樓而欠債。<br />\n<br />\nBernstein 解釋，中國青年能夠如此高速上車，是多得「父母銀行」的眷顧，「一如其他調查，在 700 位 18 至 29 歲的受訪者中總有一些網絡百萬富翁。可是，不論是一線、二線還是三線城市，那些擁有物業又沒負債的青年，都是依靠父母的金錢置業。」他又指，「跨代財富轉移（Intergenerational wealth transfer）的現象不單是理論和預測，而是正在發生。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.cup.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/china_property_1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F06%2Fchina_property_1.png&h=9735471e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.cup.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/china_property_2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F06%2Fchina_property_2.png&h=19ba40fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Bernstein</span></strong> 認為，報告對中國經濟來說是好消息，因為它反映中國不會因人們供款能力下降而出現房債泡沫爆破。「這使我們對中國房地產市場的發展變得樂觀。目前，外界不少聲音認為中國最有可能爆破的泡沫就是物業市場，尤其是一線城市的物業市場。」<br />\n<br />\n他補充，「樓價可負擔指數（平均樓價與平均年收入的比例）不但較去年上升三分之二，居住在二、三線城市的市民負擔能力亦都提升。從受訪者的數據可見，居住在一線城市的青年較有可能在 29 歲前擁有自己的物業。」<br />\n<br />\n這份報告除了是衡量中國經濟在來年會否「支爆」的指標，也是對香港青年的最大諷刺。香港的樓價冠絕世界，全球共知，數之不盡的港人，分幾十年才供完（幾）百呎樓，這些悲慘生活，在真正贏在起跑線的中國青年眼中，應是完全無法理解的人生。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cup.com.hk/2016/07/04/many-young-people-in-china-own-their-houses-debt-free/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2F2016%2F07%2F04%2Fmany-young-people-in-china-own-their-houses-debt-free%2F&d=Q8pdFaTDdXkZv1Z8oTHUCWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=a107a157\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cup.com.hk/2016/07/04/many-young-people-in-china-own-their-houses-debt-free/</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n舊登有條友個user呢就係叫Bernstein, 人民幣大好友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nB乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dbf1457f027d2abb44cb3051623b3c8be6f0c02","tid":446993,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T13:38:06.000Z","msg":"你試下外省人去買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一年唔洗強拍強拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n支那咩都假<br />\n乜都係講關係<br />\n你老豆係官/商/廠中高層<br />\n要有間屋有幾難<br />\n大把人爭住送<br />\n<br />\n你係外省農民工<br />\n咁就等食屎啦<br />\n係工廠過住監躉咁既生活"},{"pid":"8cee8f66f29a711ae3eeada667ef72b6edc0c090","tid":446993,"uid":129573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T13:39:31.000Z","msg":"租平就真"},{"pid":"2507a6f93fe9d7a08cf864c08ebdf9aa8cb2af77","tid":446993,"uid":132485,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T21:14:09.000Z","msg":"所以香港人真係要爭氣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe4aae2073e5466f5d60bfbae74fa32f97153520","tid":446993,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T21:31:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你試下外省人去買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一年唔洗強拍強拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n支那咩都假<br />\n乜都係講關係<br />\n你老豆係官/商/廠中高層<br />\n要有間屋有幾難<br />\n大把人爭住送<br />\n<br />\n你係外省農民工<br />\n咁就等食屎啦<br />\n係工廠過住監躉咁既生活</blockquote><br />\n點止監躉。女嘅要做埋雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80162a598ecda7959f8009ef5cc5e80ae9de8bf8","tid":446993,"uid":90609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T21:58:01.000Z","msg":"通常有樓都係上一代買落<br />\n到而家經濟起飛 呢一代受惠<br />\n佢地基本上唔洗點俾家用"},{"pid":"1e5daf372b756e7299ed4e5fde666cb2dfa67af7","tid":446993,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T22:03:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/27/060311_a33b7d50623193b5ed3704c06bcc67f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F27%2F060311_a33b7d50623193b5ed3704c06bcc67f2.jpg&h=781317d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a19cede79ce6a0685bee8ae81fb500ed50a0887","tid":446993,"uid":27830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T22:35:39.000Z","msg":"上個月先有個愛國商人張宇十億地<br />\n比政府強拍強買<br />\n而家仲吹奏支那買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"225da47edb855ab0012ba1be807e74cc124a50f1","tid":446993,"uid":96486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T22:47:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>會唔會畀中共強收樓先？<br />\n佢哋話發展就是硬道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家大陸收樓收地政府比錢<br />\n大把農民變土豪<br />\n邊似得港共<br />\n燒樓強拆收地<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你講依家係幾時開始？<br />\n我前排仲聽到村民同公安打架嘅news喎</blockquote><br />\n真係睇個官貪幾多， 怕煩唔算大貪又可以賺大錢咪賠得多人地自然自願搬走， 有d就賺得少貪多d山高皇帝遠咪強拆賠都唔洗賠</blockquote><br />\n你估咁多暴發戶點黎？"},{"pid":"f9269b2561f1ed97d9f61a370186f73af309902f","tid":446993,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T22:52:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>通常有樓都係上一代買落<br />\n到而家經濟起飛 呢一代受惠<br />\n佢地基本上唔洗點俾家用</blockquote><br />\n結婚d禮金，酒席又係屋企人出，所以d月光旅20頭都已經結婚<br />\n依家一夠18歲考左牌屋企人又買埋車比佢地"},{"pid":"5f0b445735d2d231c6b7c1680d73a925f428f486","tid":446993,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T22:55:13.000Z","msg":"以呢個新聞既意思,簡單來講,香港搞到而家咁都係老一代問題"},{"pid":"ec3d856f62f0aadc8f9dabd92340b79c4d7352e2","tid":446993,"uid":81052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T22:55:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">房子是用來住的，不是用來炒的</span><br />\n習近平原來係講俾香港聽，唔係講中國<br />\n<br />\n中國幾年前套劇集蝸居原來都係講香港"},{"pid":"6d66b15447412e458e0d3c110d7bad9a20672892","tid":44